2010-03-01  Thomas Moulard  <thomas.moulard@gmail.com>

	Upgrade to RobOptim core 0.5.6.

        CAUTION: starting from now, $(libdir)/roboptim-core /MUST/
        be in your LT_LIBRARY_PATH! It is also recommended to remove
        manually your old $(libdir)/roboptim-core-ipopt* files.

